'''Locus''' (plural loci)
# A [[place]] or [[locality]], especially a [[centre]] of [[activity]] or the [[scene]] of a [[crime]].
#: The cafeteria was the '''locus''' of activity.
# ([[mathematics]]) The [[set]] of all [[point]]s whose [[coordinate]]s [[satisfy]] a given [[equation]] or set of [[condition]].
